data.description: Come see this new beautiful home. Need some TLC/minor repairs. Buyers bring your vision and your own touch to this house. Quiet screened in back porch. Nice wood back yard with trees to shade. Bring your swing & lounge chairs to enjoy the peaceful wooded view from your own Custom screened back porch...waterproof laminate flooring in main living areas, carpet in Bathrooms, Family size Great Room with stone fireplace...stained wainscoting ...Vaulted ceiling in Kitchen, dining areas and GR ...built in bench seating in breakfast area, double sinks, sep. shower and garden tub in Master Bath, Vaulted ceiling in Master BR...All of this just minutes from shopping...easy route to I-20...Quite neighborhood near Honey Creek. If you buy this house...you can golf at Honey Creek Golf and Country Club; you can take the kids and your lovely pets to Johnson Park; you can head over to Arabia Mountain National Heritage Area. For all you garden and outdoor lovers: you can enjoy yourself some nice scenery at The Lewis Vaughn Botanical Gardens. After work, you can treat yourself at The Upper Hand Day Spa. Plenty of Eateries: Bailey's Restaurant & Lounge (seafoods); SUDO BAR & GRILL (CONYERS).   If you love crab boils and lobsters, you will love Coaxum's Low Country Cuisine. You can enjoy yourself some Mexican food at:   Los Charros Mexican Restaurant...just minutes from I-20; just 15 minutes from the mall, 35 minutes from Atlanta Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport; 35 minutes from downtown Atlanta. Come make this house your dream home.
